data.name: chkUnattended.ToolTip
data.value: Checking this will cause the bot to go into unattended mode. This change happens immediately and does not require clicking the Apply Settings button

data.name: chkChatter.ToolTip
data.value: Check this to turn on the Chatter AI bot (responds to whispers and says)

data.name: chkHumanCheck.ToolTip
data.value: Turns on or off Human Checking. When a player is encounterd more than once after 5 minutes, your toon will perform a random hello/acknowledge emote

data.name: cmdApplySettings.ToolTip
data.value: Applies all settings in the Rhabot Settings section. Settings are saved to disk and are implemented in the bot

data.name: txtLowAttack.ToolTip
data.value: Number of levels below you to attack. If you are 20, and this is set to 5, you will target units down to level 15

data.name: txtHighAttack.ToolTip
data.value: Number of levels above you to attack. If you are 20, and this is set to 5, you will target units up to level 25

data.name: txtSearchRange.ToolTip
data.value: Number of yards off the trail to search for hostile units / herbs /mines / chests

data.name: txtStuckTimeout.ToolTip
data.value: Global Setting - Time to wait, in seconds, before a stuck error is raised. This is the amount of time the toon remains stuck before the location is flagged stuck and a special error is raised.

data.name: chkLogoutStuck.ToolTip
data.value: Global Setting - Logs out your bot when the Stuck error is raised. The bot tries to stone home, first

data.name: txtTargetRange.ToolTip
data.value: Distnace, in yards, to be from hostile before initiating pull

data.name: txtLogoutTime.ToolTip
data.value: Automatically stones home and logs out after X minutes

data.name: txtDurability.ToolTip
data.value: When one or more items reaches this durability percent, Rhabot will return to repair vendor

data.name: chkDeclineDuel.ToolTip
data.value: Global Setting - When checked, automatically declines duels

data.name: chkDeclineGroup.ToolTip
data.value: Global Setting - When checked, automatically declines group invites

data.name: chkDeclineGuild.ToolTip
data.value: Global Setting - When checked, automatically declines guild invites

data.name: chkCharStatus.ToolTip
data.value: This allows you to view your toon's status from a remote pc, once per minute. You can view this information at http://char.rhabot.com.

data.name: chkSendOnDead.ToolTip
data.value: Sends an email to all people in your communication list (and an MSN message) when the toon dies
